  "notes": "Primary source: RFEG club page (club ALHAMA SIGNATURE, code MM29), whose 'Tarjeta de juego' tables list the recorridos as 'CONDADO DE ALHAMA - NEGRAS/BLANCAS/AMARILLAS/AZULES/ROJAS' with (M) and (F) ratings for each tee. All per-hole pars, hcp (identical allocation on the men's and women's cards for all tees) and meters were read directly from that page; every tee's 18 distances sum exactly to its published total (6884/6059/5803/5420/4997) and hcps form a permutation of 1-18. Cross-check: golfify.io per-hole distances and pars match RFEG exactly for the 6884 m and 6059 m cards, but golfify uses an older card: tee names shifted one color (its 'Blancas'=6884 m card that RFEG now labels Negras), older Azules (5741 m) and Rojas (5234 m) totals, older ratings (e.g. 77.4/140 for 6884 m) and a different stroke-index allocation (e.g. SI 14 on hole 1). The RFEG allocation returned here is the current official one. mscorecard.com and the club website scorecard page were unreachable (403/404)."
